      "text": "<p>Vasa <code>blue-box</code> klasa treba da postavi <code>margin</code> na <code>-15px</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const blueBox = document.querySelector('.blue-box');\nconst marginTop = window.getComputedStyle(blueBox)[\"margin-top\"]; \nassert.strictEqual(marginTop, \"-15px\"); "
